    # SNc DOPAMINE WISPS — PointInstancer Animation
    # Moved to layers/_dopamine_block.usda (generated by gen_dopamine_anim.py).
    # That layer is the strongest sublayer in basal_ganglia.usda / basal_ganglia_hq.usda.
